text: Josef Kutheil (born 17 April 1939) is a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Jindřichův Hradec District
